testcase.title: Check unique target id's are returned

steps.title: I am authenticated user accessing "SOAP" API
I pass a "query = JOINED(structures%3ASSS(SMILES%2C%22c1ccc2c(c1)cc%5BnH%5D2%22)) and hits = 100" as parameter to "GetPharmacologyStructureResultsV2_DrugDesignAPI" operation
I call poll async "180" times with interval "1" seconds I should get the response
response contains unique values in attribute "searchResults.pharmacologyResult.activityPharmacologicalTargetIds.targetId"
